Package tage.ai.behaviortrees

Class BTSequence

java.lang.Object
tage.ai.behaviortrees.BTBehavior
tage.ai.behaviortrees.BTComposite
tage.ai.behaviortrees.BTSequence
public class BTSequence extends BTComposite
A BTSequence node is a BTComposite that executes its child nodes from left to right. If a failure happens at any of the child nodes then the BTSequence fails. If all child nodes succeed then the BTSequence succeeds. You are basically ANDing all of the return Status's of Behaviors together.
